set current screen "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==================================================================

NAME
----

set current screen - Set the current screen object

SYNOPSIS
--------

Set the current screen object

USAGE
-----

` <?php set_current_screen( $id ); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$id` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Screen id, optional.
    Default: empty string

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [3.0](/Version_3.0 "Version 3.0")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`set_current_screen()` is located in `wp-admin/includes/template.php`

